1146075aef86019b","tid":1813592,"uid":277054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T12:22:03.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">手足好珍貴<br />\n唔好再捉鬼<br />\n<br />\n愛國愛黨<br />\n咪嚟香港<br />\n<br />\n大人齊罷工<br />\n細路唔使衝</span></div>"},{"pid":"f518a5d587f49022834d7738424e722a92d7ab67","tid":1813592,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T12:23:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2762ce3fca7090d1d5a0f1e7ce0af237099e3c9","tid":1813592,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T12:24:05.000Z","msg":"【第貳拾期牆紙】 破局<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1804841/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1804841/page/1</a><br />\nTG : <a href=\"https://t.me/WallPaperENews\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FWallPaperENews&d=bwUHcV0Pscj1NrVo4Cy%2FDe6cow1LS9WQT%2BeJ8I%2F17x8%3D&h=511d722b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/WallPaperENews</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aypmVes.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaypmVes.jpg&h=462652b7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"587a746c24c14e34d870870e75eddaa2c5eafaf8","tid":1813592,"uid":35348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T12:29:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}